{"type": "article", "id": 24374, "title": "隐藏开关的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 87, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140259ixmNUa4qwJ60CXfQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组灯是用木头和黄铜做的，它们都通过滑动来控制开关。落地灯以圆形金属片和两个小圆柱为支点，从其中一个支点换到另一个支点时就完成了开关。其余三盏桌灯与此同理，可以滑动圆形金属或者木头本身，增加了人与灯的互动和联系，也让最日常的东西多了一份趣味。设计者来自墨西哥，<a href=\"http://www.esrawe.com/product/prima-materia/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140255SLmaOgutXI4HlqVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.13034188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140256dPNvjR87xW6Furpw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140256xWAcGXujyaT1M6Ze.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140257O6IsrBkUZF2vJS1C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140257g23VQzSaARBrsi45.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}